## üö® CRITICAL RULES (Never Violate)

### Styling Rules (MANDATORY)
```scss
// ‚úÖ ALWAYS use Material Design system variables
background-color: var(--mat-sys-surface);
color: var(--mat-sys-on-surface);

// ‚úÖ ALWAYS use rem() function for ALL dimensions
padding: rem(16);
font-size: rem(14);

// ‚ùå NEVER use hardcoded colors or pixel values
background-color: #ffffff;  // ‚ùå FORBIDDEN
padding: 16px;              // ‚ùå FORBIDDEN

// ‚ùå NEVER use inline styles
<div style="padding: 20px">  // ‚ùå FORBIDDEN
```

### Angular 21+ Patterns (MANDATORY)
```typescript
// ‚úÖ ALWAYS use standalone components
@Component({ standalone: true })

// ‚úÖ ALWAYS use inject() function
private service = inject(MyService);

// ‚úÖ ALWAYS use signals for state
count = signal(0);

// ‚úÖ ALWAYS use new control flow syntax
@if (condition) { }
@for (item of items(); track item.id) { }
```

### Internationalization (MANDATORY)
```html
<!-- ‚úÖ ALWAYS use translate pipe for ALL text -->
<h1>{{ 'WELCOME_MESSAGE' | translate }}</h1>

<!-- ‚ùå NEVER hardcode text -->
<h1>Welcome to AUM</h1>  <!-- ‚ùå FORBIDDEN -->
```

### Language Switching Order (CRITICAL)
```typescript
// ‚úÖ Language switching must be LAST in event handlers
onMenuSelect(item: MenuItem) {
  if (item.value === 'compact') { /* UI Scale first */ }
  if (item.value === 'light') { /* Theme second */ }
  if (item.value === 'en') { /* Language LAST */ }
}
```

